These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, boat
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | malaysian |
| Sport         | biathlon | climbing    |
| Transport     | bike     | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, ship
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the nigerian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | cola   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian  |
| Transport     | ship   | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, documentary
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | dancing   | rock-climbing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | sports  |
| Sport         | rowing   | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: garlic, mango
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, car
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | garlic | mango |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster   | martial-arts   |
| Transport     | car       | van      |

