.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, banana
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, scientist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the paramedic##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | banana | cucumber     |
| Job     | scientist | paramedic |
| Sport   | water-polo | swimming    |

 #################################

 
