.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, plum
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, reading
2 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | plum | strawberry  |
| Hobby   | reading | woodworking |
| Pet     | turtle  | ferret     |

