.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, argentine
2 different pets are kept: cat, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the spanish is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | traveling | magic-tricks |
| Nationality   | spanish     | argentine     |
| Pet           | hamster          | cat     |

